The paper deals with privacy-preserving mechanisms for disclosing training data, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses information theoretic measures to develop these mechanisms, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses experiments on image datasets, which is a topic that falls under the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and computer vision (cs.CV).
